<plot>Based on a nationally publicized true story, Copperhead Road is a deeply affecting, no-holds-barred depiction of a drunken woman's nightmarish, post-New Year's Eve Party run-in with a sociopathic cop. It depicts with raw honesty the all too common actions of law enforcement officers who abuse their power and take the law into their own hands.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?115339</url></doc>
